00:20:38.945 --> 00:20:42.945
how [INAUDIBLE] does the process
of [INAUDIBLE] certification

00:20:42.945 --> 00:20:43.538
[INAUDIBLE]

00:20:43.538 --> 00:20:45.580
PHILIP GREENSPUN: If you
build your own airplane?

00:20:45.580 --> 00:20:46.480
AUDIENCE: Yeah.

00:20:46.480 --> 00:20:49.532
PHILIP GREENSPUN: My friend
