00:21:15.100 --> 00:21:16.785
in the experimental world.

00:21:16.785 --> 00:21:18.160
It's never been
attractive to me.

00:21:18.160 --> 00:21:21.590
I mean, if you talk to the
people who do experimentals,

00:21:21.590 --> 00:21:24.040
they're really passionate
about building and tinkering.

00:21:24.040 --> 00:21:27.550
They actually have very
few hours of flight time

00:21:27.550 --> 00:21:28.720
accumulated.

00:21:28.720 --> 00:21:31.000
And that becomes a problem,
because their pilot--

00:21:31.000 --> 00:21:33.790
even if they were a good
pilot when they started,

00:21:33.790 --> 00:21:38.080
after spending 13 years
in a garage building,

00:21:38.080 --> 00:21:39.580
their pilot skills
are pretty rusty.

